Title: front cover
Description.caption: Abstract of title to Rancho San Jose de Buenos Ayres.  Belongs to Los Angeles and Santa Monica Land and Water Co.; John Wolfskill Estate, E. E. Hall, Secty

Title: page 53 map 1
Description.note: Plat map of Rancho San Jose de Buenos Ayres, confirmed to Benjamin D. Wilson, measuring 31 x 36 cm., with a scale of 40 chains to 1 inch; surveyed by Henry Hancock, Sept. 1858

Title: page 123 map 2
Description.note: Map of the subdivisions of Rancho San Jose de Buenos Ayres, measuring 33 x 22 cm, with a scale of 400 feet to 1 inch, reduced to 600 ft.; surveyed by Theo C. Keeberlee in 1887
